<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ880219-0142 </DOCNO><HL> Who's News: News Corp. </HL><SO> </SO><CO> WNEWS NWS </CO><DATELINE> NEWS Corp.  </DATELINE><TEXT>   Leon Hertz, former vice president and associate publisher of the New York Post, was named vice president, global marketing, of this Australian media, entertainment and printing concern controlled by Rupert Murdoch. In his new post, Mr. Hertz will oversee international advertising sales. He also will remain executive vice president of the News America Publishing Inc. unit. </TEXT></DOC>